definitions.title: vb. pass over, away
definitions.body: (Ar. ja0za pass by, over; Aram. [[גּוּז]] cross, goz pass away, fail—

definitions.title: Qal
definitions.body: Pf [[גׇּז]] Ps 90:10; Impf. [[וַיׇּ֫גׇז]] Nu 11:31; —pass away, of the life of the aged, Ps 90:10 [[גׇּז חִישׁ]]; trans. bring over, subj. wind, obj. quails fr. sea, Nu 11:31 (rd. perh. Hiph. [[וַיׇּגֶז]] cf. Kö:i. 442 Di).
